
''Embarrassment of Riches'' is an 6-song "albumette" by [[Elephant Micah]] which will be released on [[September 29]], [[2006]] on Micah's own [[LRRC (Luddite Rural Recording Cooperative)|LRRC]] label. The record will be unveiled at a record release party at Micah's alma mater, [[Earlham College]]. No details about the tracklist are yet known.

